rated into a computational\nbiomechanical framework, with several numerical examples verifying accuracy and\ncomputational efficiency of the method, including in an analytic test, in an\nanalytic fractional differential equation, as well as in a computational\nbiomechanical model problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Oct 2019 20:55:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
